description:
Folding chairs are a practical choice for social activities and for everyday use in the home. Folding chairs offer a simple and compact storage solution. This portable chair can be used in a variety of indoor or outdoor events. This Hercules Folding Chair was built to take on heavy usage with an 18 gauge steel frame, triple braced and leg strengthening support bars. After an event you can stack them on top of each other or in a row. To make transporting even easier, equip yourself with the appropriate sized folding chair dolly to make event management more effortless.
